{"tid":1233233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔係想講鬼定唔鬼，但而家見到留守嘅人咁少","createTime":"2019-06-16T17:54:40.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T18:15:03.000Z","uid":218575,"like":46,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5aafab381ebb6fda091594ed1176df7abd4bdccf","tid":1233233,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:54:40.000Z","msg":"請問衝乜？<br />\n星期一唔會開送中條例會<br />\n衝完有咩作用？下一步係點？<br />\n<br />\n仲要6/12人數比今晚留守人數多<br />\n都俾警犬驅散到<br />\n你而家得咁少人可以做到乜野？<br />\n唔信嘅自己睇立場新聞<br />\n睇下今晚留守嘅人有幾多<br />\n<br />\n再講一次 無話要捉鬼 <br />\n我只係想講 你咁少人<br />\n衝完好快俾警犬驅散<br />\n駁俾警犬拉？<br />\n定你地覺得<br />\n而家即時可以召集到6/12咁嘅今數出黎？"},{"pid":"cf416d912168295580d36035a6373688af289224","tid":1233233,"uid":247639,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:55:23.000Z","msg":"G持肥仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bff00f892f4a434afa1cf3ca8fe789c038073008","tid":1233233,"uid":143210,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:55:41.000Z","msg":"而家係和理非嘅回合！！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1233067\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1233067</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n唱歌嘅時候就係夜晚<br />\n<br />\n衝嘅時候就係日頭"},{"pid":"6ce2897a410f230dcd679354ef7221a5e0f0a6cc","tid":1233233,"uid":238801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:56:11.000Z","msg":"梨趕得好岩牙！"},{"pid":"15ee5162f1a74fd3869c5279865a439ff1a3f5e1","tid":1233233,"uid":258055,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:56:15.000Z","msg":"夜晚衝意義不大 市民訓哂覺 記者又少 入黑又混亂<br />\n要衝留番日頭 唔可以再浪費每一個義士既心機<br />\n<br />\n夜晚適合唱聖詩<br />\n<br />\n利伸發夢"},{"pid":"8927611d71ea20b671aab10962e6e5f046f1bd94","tid":1233233,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T17:57:05.000Z","msg":"唔衝好簡單, 唔知後續係乜, 亦無統一訴求, 人少都係重點"},{"pid":"0f42f296db72bb7ecddbbd244ddf774a6ce50eda","tid":1233233,"uid":218575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf4